Conquer space like never before! Welcome to Space XY! BGaming is happy to introduce the brand new type of game, where you have to hop on a virtual space rocket and fly to eternal height!

Watch your rocket fly over X and Y coordinates. Make bets and fly your spacecraft to the stars! Make multiple bets, reach top multipliers and get big winnings. But be cautious, you have to jump off the rocket before it flies away into deep space. This is the only way for you to get incredible winnings. Get ready to launch, eternity awaits!

The game’s goal is to win money by jumping off the rocket until it disappears in deep space! The winning is the bet multiplied by the coefficient shown on the screen at the moment you jump out of the rocket. You win only if you cash out before the rocket disappears!
